title: Honey Mustard Roast Chicken - Food Wishes
description:
Now only are you going to learn how to make a delicious honey mustard marinade/glaze recipe for chicken, you’re also going to see one of the easiest, and most effective poultry techniques of all time, spatchcocking That it’s also super fun to say is just a bonus.

For the fully formatted, printable, written recipe, follow this link:
